nodes.text: Sleeft Docking Bay Maintenance was a transport company based in the city of Mos Eisley on the planet Tatooine. They controlled several cargo storage units near the Mos Eisley Spaceport. At some point, they attempted to steal a shipment of droid parts from the Notsub Shipping Company, but the shipment fell into the hands of the Bith Angor Farn instead. One of Sleeft's directors was Coral Ohah.
